---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="McGennis Family Blog - Jefferson City, Missouri Stories & Updates"
  description="Read the latest from the McGennis family in Jefferson City, Missouri. Business insights, family updates, community stories, and more from Caleb and Stephanie McGennis."
>
  <section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-32 px-4 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        McGennis Family Blog
      </h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-mcgennis-gold mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-500 font-light">
        Stories, insights, and updates from Jefferson City's most notable family
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 font-light">
          Welcome to our blog! Here we'll share stories about entrepreneurship, family life, ministry work,
          and our journey in Jefferson City, Missouri.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Coming Soon Message -->
      <div class="bg-white p-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-mcgennis-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
          Blog Posts Coming Soon!
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-8 font-light">
          We're working on bringing you great content about our businesses, family adventures, and life in Jefferson City.
          Check back soon for exciting updates!
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Upcoming Topics:</h3>
          <ul class="text-left max-w-md mx-auto space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-mcgennis-gold mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Building Businesses in Jefferson City</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-mcgennis-gold mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Balancing Entrepreneurship and Family Life</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-mcgennis-gold mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Ministry Work with Sports Crusaders</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-mcgennis-gold mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Jefferson City Community Events</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-mcgennis-gold mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Behind the Scenes of Our Ventures</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-mcgennis-gold mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Tech Tips from dr4g0nbyt3</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Newsletter Signup -->
      <div class="mt-16 bg-gray-50 p-10 text-center border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Stay Updated!</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8 text-gray-500 font-light">
          Want to be notified when we publish new blog posts? Follow us on social media!
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/calebmichaelmcgennis" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-mcgennis-navy text-white font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
            Follow Caleb on Facebook
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/stephanie.davis.900388" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-medium tracking-wide hover:border-mcgennis-navy hover:text-mcgennis-navy transition-all duration-300">
            Follow Stephanie on Facebook
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Topics -->
  <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
          What We'll Be Writing About
        </h2>
        <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-mcgennis-gold mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="group bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 hover:border-mcgennis-navy">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-mcgennis-navy group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Business & Entrepreneurship</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            Insights from building and running multiple businesses in Jefferson City, including successes,
            challenges, and lessons learned.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 hover:border-mcgennis-gold">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-mcgennis-gold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Family Life</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            Stories about raising Leonardo and Raphael, family adventures, and balancing work and family
            in Central Missouri.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 hover:border-mcgennis-maroon">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-mcgennis-maroon group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Ministry & Community</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            Updates from Sports Crusaders ministry, community service projects, and our faith journey
            in Jefferson City.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
